SubjectIssuance of two $2 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 100th anniversary of the birth of Bill Reid
PrecisOrder Authorizing the ISSUANCE of two $2 circulation coins with a design commemorating the 100th anniversary of the of the birth of Bill Reid in order to serve as tangible keepsakes of an iconic representation of Indigenous art and culture.
